P3b was evoked by Probe stimuli in both the Lines and Clock task. Similarly to P3a, P3b amplitudes also diminished during spaceflight. The four-factor rANOVA [Session (1:9) × Task (Lines, Clock) × Region (Frontal, Central, Centroparietal, Parietal) × Laterality (Left, Midline, Right)] (Fig. 3C,D,E, Supplementary Figs. S8, S9, S10C,D) disclosed a significant Session main effect [F(8,32) = 4.92, P = 0.04, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
